---
title: Chermoula-Spiced Chicken & Veggie Couscous with Lemony Garlic Dip & Almonds
description: It’s fresh, flavourful, and a fan-favourite especially with chermoula spices and a fluffy (another ‘f’ word) couscous, it’s a chicken dish we can all become fans of. Zest it up with a garlic dip for fragrance (okay, that’s the last one) and that’s dinner finished (sorry).

*We’ve replaced the radish in this recipe with cucumber due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
